          <title>Luka scores 29 points and LeBron adds 17 in the Lakers' 2nd straight win over the Clippers, 108-102</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LOS ANGELES (AP) — Luka Doncic had 29 points and nine assists, LeBron James added 17 points and the Los Angeles Lakers hung on to beat the Los Angeles Clippers for the second time in three days, 108-102 on Sunday night.]]></description>
